sentences: She has held this position since 1999.
In 1976, she was selected to represent India at a jazz vocalists festival in Warsaw, Poland.
She returned to India in 1993 and began performing with Louis Banks, Sanjay Divecha, Gerard Machado, and Keith Peters
She formed her own band in 2009.
Their first album, was produced independently and was released in September 2012.
More Men On My MindIn January 2022, Radha Thomas started a podcast, The Indie Dog.

Between June 2020 and June 2021, Radha Thomas produced and performed in 52 jazz videos which, significantly, amounts to one video a week for a year.
She moved to New York, where she lived for twenty years.
Besides writing the lyrics for all the original material she performs, she has written, mostly in a humorous vein for the Bangalore Monthly, a column called "Between the Sexes."
Her work has been published in The Hindu, Man's World, Explocity.com, Bangalore Mirror, Asian Age, and Bangalore Monthly.
